{"id":71763,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/公民社会与ngo发展周刊（103）/","date":"2010-05-12T09:00:28Z","modified":"2010-05-12T09:00:28Z","title":"公民社会与NGO发展周刊（103）","content":"<div>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><strong><span>本期特别关注：一：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">512</span></span><span>大地震特别专辑；二：玉树大地震中的僧侣；三：成都西郊河加盖事件再起大波；四：希望小学食堂状况</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span>我一直重申的是：欢迎各</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">NGO</span></span><span>组织和有心人提供诸种信得过的信息，每条信息的真伪，请实际参与者进一步自行核实。请注意，我不直接接受任何捐款和财物，我也不负责钱物的中转工作，我只负责给各位牵线搭桥。我的工作邮箱是</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> <span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"https://newdesai.appspot.com/?url=aGNyS%2BKE%5E4R%5Extg.Pz5YcesP%60R6wpoL8%3Am%5C-%5CLr%40t%5BnLyKxu%5CV.%3FNoUqMvv%5Dj%5BzRe%2CfFABZNRH%2C7%3ER2q%5DV5gHd%3E%5D%3ErO%3E\">lijuhantian@sina.com</a> </span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><strong><span>一：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">512</span></span></strong><span><strong>大地震特别专辑。</strong>明天就是</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">512</span></span><span>大地震两周年的忌日，请我们不要忘记这些无辜的死难者，特别是豆腐渣校舍下的冤魂。两周年了，政府不公布死难者名单，没有像样子的纪念，但我们却必须记住。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span></span><span>）：川震血的教訓</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>解密著作曝光</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>三度預測強度不獲理</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>老專家﹕預了被打壓。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100509/4/hwo9.html\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://hk.news.yahoo.com/article/100509/4/hwo9.html</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span></span><span>）：外国人真的不怕地震传言？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.gongyishibao.com/news/newsshow.asp?id=3515\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.gongyishibao.com/news/newsshow.asp?id=3515</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span></span><span>）：四川</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5.12</span></span><span>汶川大地震灾后两年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">SQR</span></span><span>访谈研究总结。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://sichuan-quake-relief.org/zw/2010/05/sichuan5-12wenchuandadizhenanhouliangnian-sqr-fangtanyanjiuzongjie/\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://sichuan-quake-relief.org/zw/2010/05/sichuan5-12wenchuandadizhenanhouliangnian-sqr-fangtanyanjiuzongjie/</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span><span>）：不抓豆腐渣</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>打压可怜人</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>禁上访申诉</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>苦家长不惜拚死求公道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gbindex.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gbindex.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5</span></span><span>）：喪子聚源中學家長周興容﹕「我思念的是炸藥與槍」。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba2.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba2.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>）：喪子北川中學家長姜勇﹕「明遺址拜祭</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>誰也阻不了！」</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba3.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba3.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7</span></span><span>）：丧子都江堰新建小学家长俞清：“政府做好，谁愿意闹？“。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba4.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba4.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">8</span></span><span>）：丧女富新二小家长刘小英：前线家长遭污蔑分化。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba5.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba5.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">9</span></span><span>）：谭作人妻子：愈打压维权</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>人民愈对立。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba6.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://news.mingpao.com/20100511/gba6.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">10</span></span><span>）：黄琦强调维权不变</span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"> </span><span>网民“念念不忘”齐行动。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/hq-05042010094359.html\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/hq-05042010094359.html</span></a></span><span>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><strong><span>二：南都周刊：僧侣下险山。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.nbweekly.com/print/article/10268_0.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.nbweekly.com/print/article/10268_0.shtml</span></a></span></strong><span><strong>。</strong>玉树大地震中僧侣的诸多贡献，为官方遮盖掩藏，但你只要有自己的眼睛和耳朵，只要有一颗寻求真相的心，你就不会不知道僧侣在这次大地震救援中，以及将来的灾后重建中的特殊作用。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><strong>三：成都西郊河加盖事件再起大波。</strong>政府几次三番意欲在城内的河流上加盖、修建高架桥，这对城市环境的破坏是必然的。为什么遭遇如此多的反对，他们还要强行上马，那就只能用官商勾结的利益来作解释了。一座城市被弄得满目疮痍，还大言不惭地说自己在建设田园城市，真是得了官方几十年撒谎的精髓。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span></span><span>）：关于西郊河加盖，华西和商报哪个在说谎？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/284/194843.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/284/194843.shtml</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span></span><span>）：活水公园设计者：西郊河上架桥不明智。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.wccdaily.com.cn/epaper/hxdsb/html/2010-05/09/content_187047.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.wccdaily.com.cn/epaper/hxdsb/html/2010-05/09/content_187047.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span></span><span>）：西郊河加盖：难以逃脱的宿命？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.wccdaily.com.cn/epaper/hxdsb/html/2010-05/08/content_186930.htm\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.wccdaily.com.cn/epaper/hxdsb/html/2010-05/08/content_186930.htm</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span><span>）：<span style=\"color:black\">西郊河不再“加盖”新方案拟建高架桥。</span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black\"><a href=\"http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/284/194843.shtml\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://bbs.city.tianya.cn/tianyacity/Content/284/194843.shtml</span></a></span><span style=\"color:black\">。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black\"></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><strong><span>四：希望小学食堂及学生伙食状况调查报告。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.gongyishibao.com/news/newsshow.asp?id=3483&amp;title=msyw\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.gongyishibao.com/news/newsshow.asp?id=3483&amp;title=msyw</span></a></span></strong><span><strong>。</strong>希望小学的硬件如校舍的质量，一般说来，受到人们的关注。但一所学校好坏，其软件如师资、图书馆乃至就餐环境、餐饮质量，亦是非同小可。这次《公益时报》作了一个关于希望小学食堂及学生伙食状况的调查，虽样本偏少，地区间亦不够平衡，但其开启对学生食堂的重视是值得嘉许的。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><strong>五：灾后重建及其它招募和需求信息。（</strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span></span><span>）：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5.12</span></span><span>灾区</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">16</span></span><span>个阳光生活社区中心招募合作伙伴。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.npi.org.cn/newsshow.php?pid=766\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.npi.org.cn/newsshow.php?pid=766</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">2</span></span><span>）：青海玉树震后，则热福利院孩子进京，欢迎同城衣物捐助。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.douban.com/event/11783191/\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.douban.com/event/11783191/</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">3</span></span><span>）：中国扶贫基金会招募万名志愿者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2151\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2151</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4</span></span><span>）：泓德中育灾区救援办公室急招中学教师志愿者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2152\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.chinadevelopmentbrief.org.cn/sortinfoview.php?id=2152</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">5</span></span><span>）：乐施会招聘社会性别平等项目官员（截至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>日）。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5542\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5542</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">6</span></span><span>）：自然之友城市生活垃圾项目项目招募</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">4~6</span></span><span>名志愿者。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5546\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.greengo.cn/news.php?id=5546</span></a></span><span>。（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">7</span></span><span>）：陕西妇女儿童发展基金会招聘启事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"http://www.ingo.org.cn/viewthread.php?tid=11416\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">http://www.ingo.org.cn/viewthread.php?tid=11416</span></a></span><span>。</span><span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:13.5pt\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\"></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin:0cm 0cm 0pt\"><span><strong>六：灾后重建及其它诸种信息汇集。（</strong></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman\">1</span></span><span>）四川强震两周年将届，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"f